Hi Yokees We ve listen to your feedback on the previous version and made some quick changes: Balance bar between your voice and the music is back. Fix audio glitch on some devices. Made some other bug and crash fixes. Enjoy Yokee Team

Hey Yokees! We got a huge update for you: Brand new singing player a professional audio FXs bar which allow to tune the FX parameters. Ability to mark successful points in the songs and go back to them later. Easy camera on off switch Great sharing save and sharing experience A cappella style songs Support iPad Portrait Allow to add album art and description to video and non video recordings iOS 10 compatibility Get notified when your recording is ready! Many more fixes and enhancements. Happy Singing!

Hey folks! We got a huge update for you: Songbook redesign which include songs previews and artwork. On boarding flow to help you choose the right songs to sing. Recommended playlist with songs which match your singing history. Cool new Video FXs GLING 80s SCI FI and Animation . Back camera support for video. Realtime indications when your lighting is too bright or dark during video. Realtime indication when your mic volume is too low. Please keep sending us feedback at support yokee.tv

Hey singers We have a huge update for you with dozens of new features and improvments. New tab bar navigation to make it easier to access the app sections. New Performances feed tab with the hottest covers created by users in the Yokee Community. We ve redesigned our lyrics player and added support to both portrait and landscape. New user account section to make sure your recording are always safe. You can now change the name and album art of your video recording before saving or sharing it. New Fire video theme

Are you ready for the Holidays Yokee Karaoke is. We ve branded the app for Christmas and added a special Christmas playlist for you to sing. We ve also optimize the app for iOS8 iPhone6 and iPhone6 Lastly we added a new Chorus sound effect we hope you ll love it. Happy Holidays!

Hi Singers we ve got a major update for you! There s a brand new player and we are so proud of it. We ve added on screen feedback for your singing and new Sound Effects to make your signing experience more fun. We ve fixed few more issues to assure compatibility with iOS8. This version also support iOS6 users so now everybody can enjoy the latest Yokee app re design.
This version is quick yet very important one. We solved various song loading problems and made some under the hood fixes to make your singing experience better!
We ve been listening to your feedback! This quick version improve the app stability after the major release of Yokee s new look.

YOKEE INTRODUCES A WHOLE NEW LOOK! Biggest update yet! Yokee 3.0 is here and we are so proud of it. We ve given the app a complete makeover! Everything is cleaner smoother faster simpler and the singing experience just got better. We are confident you ll love it. We ve change a bit how the navigation works. There s a new sidebar where you can find all your recent songs recordings friends and settings ... We are already working on more improvements for the next version and can t wait to hear what you think about this one.

In this version we focused on improving the experience when connecting to external devices. You can now connect to any Bluetooth USB or AppleTV devices to sing or listen to your performances. Don t forget we are always releasing the best hit songs so check back often.
We fixed some bugs cleaned some ads and improved loading times to get you singing faster. Don t forget we re always releasing the best hit songs so check back often.

This version is a hot fix for the random crashing and microphone not working bugs that occurs on some devices. We are sorry the bug slipped past us. Thank you everyone for all your feedback and support. Reminding you we just added the following: Support external devices as speakers. You can now connect to any Bluetooth USB or AppleTV devices to sing or listen to your performances. Support recording without headphones. For best recording quality we still recommend to use headphones.

Hi Singers! we ve got a brand new update for you! We ve been listening to your feedback! In this update we focused on major audio improvements: Support external devices as speakers. You can now connect to any Bluetooth USB or AppleTV devices to sing or listen to your performances. Support recording without headphones. For best recording quality we still recommend to use headphones.
